short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring back the Show YouTube Dislike Counter with this extension!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Show YouTube Dislike Counter extension brings back the removed dislike counter on YouTube. With this extension, you can once again see the number of likes and dislikes on videos, helping you better assess the quality of the content based on real user feedback. Additionally, the extension provides the following features:

✅Like / Dislike count display
✅Rating display
✅View count display

Enhance your YouTube experience with "Show YouTube Dislike Counter - Enhancer" and easily identify content worth watching.,
